Database summary and statistics

<<<<<<< Updated upstream

The number of entries in the database is 36. Most entries have multiple time-series of CO2 flux release from incubation experiments. The current total number of time series is 561, and the total number of data points is 10951.

=======

This file contains a summary of the data currently available in the soil incubation database sidb. Currently, the number of entries in the database is 36. Most entries have multiple time-series of CO2 flux release from incubation experiments. The current total number of time-series is 561, and the total number of datapoints is 10951. The last entry was added on 2017-02-07.

Datasets

The file ~/scripts/plotEntry.R can be used to plot individual entries from the database. For example

source("~/sidb/scripts/plotEntry.R")
plotEntry(entry=Andrews2000SBB)
